 null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_mini.png?m=1739322433", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_normal.png?m=1739322433", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_large.png?m=1739322433", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_xlarge.png?m=1739322433", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_xlarge.png?m=1739322433", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a4a/1a79/721257_xlarge.png?m=1739322433", "created": 1732161765, "last_modified": 1739322433}, "last_reply_by": "fionasit007", "last_touched": 1739347477, "title": "V 友们是每天都刮胡子么，有个想法，大家觉得怎么样？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1110819", "created": 1739322721, "deleted": 0, "content": "个人胡子长的特别快，每天早上都要刮，感觉很麻烦，刮胡刀，时间都是成本。\r\n考虑要不要去直接激光脱毛，这样一劳永逸，有没有研究过的老哥，听说韩国那边很多男的都这样。", "content_rendered": "<p>个人胡子长的特别快，每天早上都要刮，感觉很麻烦，刮胡刀，时间都是成本。\n考虑要不要去直接激光脱毛，这样一劳永逸，有没有研究过的老哥，听说韩国那边很多男的都这样。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1739322721, "replies": 127, "id": 1110819}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 19286, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146", "stars": 3353, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 665582, "username": "qingyingwan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/qingyingwan", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9202cf2201e9403d0f02a5d94d4dfe52?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9202cf2201e9403d0f02a5d94d4dfe52?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9202cf2201e9403d0f02a5d94d4dfe52?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1701667190, "last_modified": 1739284894}, "last_reply_by": "gotosky", "last_touched": 1739347926, "title": "八年前端分享最近两周面试情况", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1110790", "created": 1739286537, "deleted": 0, "content": "**背景**\r\n\r\n985 非科班，17 年毕业 18 年开始做前端\r\n\r\n\r\n**工作经历**\r\n\r\n18-19 小公司前端 重庆\r\n\r\n19-21 字节前端 上海\r\n\r\n21-23 美团前端 成都\r\n\r\n23 年  上海某公司呆了一周跑路\r\n\r\n23-24 快手 nodejs 服务端 北京\r\n\r\n24-25 国外创业公司 ai 全栈 远程 \r\n\r\n**面试结果**\r\n\r\n| 公司      | 介绍 | 结果     |\r\n| :---        |    :----:   |          ---: |\r\n| 海外 xx 电商独角兽      | 推荐算法后端，全问的 C++正好我会       | 已拿 offer 背调中   |\r\n| 海外 xx ai   | ai 画布创业公司，python 后端        | 三面 ceo 完了等通知      |\r\n| 海外 xx 硬件 ai   | ai 硬件应用，python 后端        | 二面过等通知      |\r\n| 海外 xx 人工智能   | 大模型开发+应用后端       | ceo 面过了，给个 homework ，不想搞      |\r\n| 月之暗面   | 大模型应用后端       | 二面挂      |\r\n\r\n**总结**\r\n\r\n后面还有好几个面试排着，没啥希望做纯前端了，没希望继续大厂了，感觉职业生涯越来越难\r\n\r\n最近 ai 方向的工作机会变多起来了，各位大佬可以开始发力了\r\n\r\n不知道为啥，国外的机会比国内多，面试通过的几率也比国内高", "content_rendered": "<p><strong>背景</strong></p>\n<p>985 非科班，17 年毕业 18 年开始做前端</p>\n<p><strong>工作经历</strong></p>\n<p>18-19 小公司前端 重庆</p>\n<p>19-21 字节前端 上海</p>\n<p>21-23 美团前端 成都</p>\n<p>23 年  上海某公司呆了一周跑路</p>\n<p>23-24 快手 nodejs 服务端 北京</p>\n<p>24-25 国外创业公司 ai 全栈 远程 </p>\n<p><strong>面试结果</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>公司</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n<th>结果</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>海外 xx 电商独角兽</td>\n<td>推荐算法后端，全问的 C++正好我会</td>\n<td>已拿 offer 背调中</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>海外 xx ai</td>\n<td>ai 画布创业公司，python 后端</td>\n<td>三面 ceo 完了等通知</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>海外 xx 硬件 ai</td>\n<td>ai 硬件应用，python 后端</td>\n<td>二面过等通知</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>海外 xx 人工智能</td>\n<td>大模型开发+应用后端</td>\n<td>ceo 面过了，给个 homework ，不想搞</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>月之暗面</td>\n<td>大模型应用后端</td>\n<td>二面挂</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table><p><strong>总结</strong></p>\n<p>后面还有好几个面试排着，没啥希望做纯前端了，没希望继续大厂了，感觉职业生涯越来越难</p>\n<p>最近 ai 方向的工作机会变多起来了，各位大佬可以开始发力了</p>\n<p>不知道为啥，国外的机会比国内多，面试通过的几率也比国内高</p>\n", "last_modified": 1739287003, "replies": 108, "id": 1110790}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1615956453", "name": "random", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1615956453", "title": "随想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/random", "topics": 3965, "footer": "", "header": "有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。", "title_alternative": "Random", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453", "stars": 1261, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 59, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 391699, "username": "dongdongdong", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dongdongdong", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ff2/4ef6/391699_mini.png?m=1727572468", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ff2/4ef6/391699_normal.png?m=1727572468", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ff2/4ef6/391699_large.png?m=1727572468", "created": 1552440275, "last_modified": 1727572468}, "last_reply_by": "xtx", "last_touched": 1739345694, "title": "刚大学室友说存了第一个 100 万了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1110752", "created": 1739275689, "deleted": 0, "content": "不知道我能不能存到，遥遥无期，太穷了", "content_rendered": "不知道我能不能存到，遥遥无期，太穷了", "last_modified": 1739275689, "replies": 108, "id": 1110752}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1615956453", "name": "random", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1615956453", "title": "随想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/random", "topics": 3965, "footer": "", "header": "有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。", "title_alternative": "Random", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453", "stars": 1261, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 59, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 657637, "username": 